WEBVTT

00:04.104 --> 00:06.405
911. What's your emergency?

00:06.407 --> 00:09.541
Um, I'm 13,
and I'm home alone,

00:09.543 --> 00:12.177
but there's this girl
who's been banging on the walls

00:12.179 --> 00:14.013
for hours in my apartment.

00:14.015 --> 00:16.749
And my mom's not home,
and I'm really scared,

00:16.751 --> 00:20.285
and I don't know what to do.

00:20.287 --> 00:22.521
911.
What's your emergency?

00:22.523 --> 00:24.356
Hi, there's a girl
in my building

00:24.358 --> 00:26.058
screaming that she's gonna
kill everyone here

00:26.060 --> 00:27.659
and that we're all out
to get her.

00:27.661 --> 00:30.696
You need to send the police.
This chick is crazy.

00:30.698 --> 00:32.798
911. What's your emergency?

00:32.800 --> 00:35.067
This is, like, the third time
that I've called this month.

00:35.069 --> 00:36.668
The bitch is crazy.

00:36.670 --> 00:39.138
Sir, please calm down.
The police are coming.

00:39.140 --> 00:40.639
Y'all need to send
someone fast

00:40.641 --> 00:43.308
before she blows this place up.
I'm serious.

00:43.310 --> 00:44.610
Yes, we have been notified

00:44.612 --> 00:45.811
by other tenants
in the building.

00:45.813 --> 00:47.446
The police are on their way.

00:54.654 --> 00:57.489
I live below her.
This is my third time calling.

00:57.491 --> 00:59.658
When are you guys
sending someone out?

00:59.660 --> 01:02.728
I don't understand
why you guys keep coming here
and nothing happens.

01:02.730 --> 01:05.330
Sir, I can't do anything
from my end.

01:05.331 --> 01:08.500
You have to stay calm and wait
for the cops to arrive please.

01:08.502 --> 01:09.668
She plays loud music

01:09.670 --> 01:11.203
and then screams
out the window

01:11.205 --> 01:12.805
and just keeps doing this
over and over.

01:12.807 --> 01:15.607
It's been going on
since 5:00 A.M. this morning.

01:15.609 --> 01:16.809
Ma'am, I understand that.

01:16.811 --> 01:18.710
Please stay inside
your apartment.

01:18.712 --> 01:21.146
The police are on their way.

01:22.817 --> 01:24.249
Hello, this is Autumn.

01:24.251 --> 01:25.818
Your sister is at it again!

01:25.820 --> 01:27.686
-You said it would stop,
and it hasn't.
-What?

01:27.688 --> 01:30.556
It's gotten worse.
I can't take it anymore!

01:30.558 --> 01:33.325
- Okay-- okay.
- -I want her gone!

01:33.327 --> 01:35.828
Please-- please, no,
don't call the police.

01:35.830 --> 01:37.429
I'll be right there.

